        "mini_practice": [
          {
            "type": "guided_speaking",
            "prompt_en": "Talk about 3 snacks or meals you ate last week. Say: what you ate, where, what you liked, what you hated.",
            "prompt_es": "Habla de 3 snacks o comidas que comiste la semana pasada: qué comiste, dónde, qué te gustó y qué odiaste.",
            "model": {
              "en": "Last week, I ate three different meals. On Monday, I ate a cheese sandwich at home. I liked it because it was simple. On Wednesday, I went to a café and ate cake and drank coffee. I loved the cake, but I hated the coffee because it was bitter. On Saturday, I ate chicken soup at my grandmother’s house. It was warm and delicious.",
              "es": "La semana pasada comí tres comidas diferentes. El lunes comí un sándwich de queso en casa. Me gustó porque era simple. El miércoles fui a un café y comí pastel y tomé café. Me encantó el pastel, pero odié el café porque era amargo. El sábado comí sopa de pollo en la casa de mi abuela. Estaba rica y calentita."
            }
          }
        ]
